  "text": "In conclusion, we have demonstrated electrical control of resonant scattering from a single QD embedded in a nano-photonic waveguide. The QD was shown to act both as a source of electrically tunable, waveguide-coupled single photons and as a nonlinear element to control photon-photon interactions in the waveguide. High purity single photon emission was demonstrated under resonant excitation with g [CITATION_1] (0)=0. [CITATION_2] . The transmission of a weak coherent laser through the waveguide was modulated by up to 40% by electrically controlling the QD-laser detuning.",
